    <td valign="top" align="left"><font face="Arial" size="3"><b><font color="#004080">CORRECTIONS</font></b>&nbsp;</font>
      <p><font size="2" face="Arial">In the Spring 2000 Centennial pullout
      section, CAPT Edward L. Beach, USN (ret.) was erroneously listed as having
      been the XO of USS <i> Tang</i> (SS-306). CAPT Beach served as the XO of USS
      <i>
      Trigger</i> (SS-237) and <i> Tirante</i> (SS-420), not Tang. UNDERSEA WARFARE regrets
      the error. In the centerfold section, USS <i> Pennsylvania</i> (SSBN-735) (GOLD)
      was inadvertently left off the Battle &quot;E&quot; winners list.
      Congratulations to officers and crew!</font></p>
